England Batting First in Opening One-Day Match Against Sri Lanka

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-06-28T12:37:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/england-batting-first-in-opening-one-day-match-against-sri-lanka.html
England  is batting first after  Sri
Lanka  won the toss and elected to field in their opening one-day
cricket match at the Oval in  London .  The start of play was delayed about 30 minutes by rain.
England won the Test series 1-0, with Sri Lanka taking a
Twenty20 match three days ago.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
